title: A Symbolic Patterned Look at Consequences of Supplanting the Masculine in Three Levels of Reality
description:
Masculine failure/dereliction is often given as the justification for an intervention that reduces the masculine presence or role. The consequences of this appear to cascade the failures at all levels of reality and should open up a conversation of how the masculine can be supported instead of supplanted.
